## Conventions

- Jest with `jest-preset-angular`
- TestBed for test module configuration
- `fixture.detectChanges()` mandatory after state changes
- `By.css()` for template queries
- `fakeAsync` + `tick` for timers and debounce
- Mock services via `providers` with `useValue`
- Standalone components imported directly
